OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start with
OL,6,Fperhaps some patchy drizzle. This
OL,7,Fclearing during the morning, then a
OL,8,Fdry day with a good number of pleasant
OL,9,Fsunny spells and feeling mild. A
OL,10,Flittle breezy by the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry this evening and
OL,13,Fovernight with prolonged clear spells
OL,14,Ffor most. Strengthening breezes around
OL,15,Fcoasts and hills. A cool night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FSome hazy sunshine possible
OL,18,Fto start Thursday, but cloud tending
OL,19,Fto thicken as the day progresses ahead
OL,20,Fof rain arriving later. Another very
OL,21,Fmild day before this.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
