OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,6,Fsettled on Friday and Saturday with
OL,7,Ffurther sunny spells, but temperatures
OL,8,Freturning to nearer average. Cloudier
OL,9,Fon Sunday with spells of rain possible.
